items.title: Trump is deploying 2,000 California National Guard troops over governor’s objections to LA to quell protests
items.description: DHS said in a statement that recent ICE operations in Los Angeles resulted in the arrest of 118 immigrants.

items.title: A hot trend in the housing market is Gen Z buying homes with siblings
items.description: BofA found that 22% of Gen Z homeowners bought their home with siblings, surging from 12% in 2024 and just 4% in 2023.
